name: Innovate Fucking Brain (pre order)
description:
This Tee is now available for pre-order.
Due to lack of funds but a strong urge to get this up and running we need your help to get these tees printed, Pick the tee you would like. After 45 days( commencing 14/02/2011 ) the T-shirt with the most pre-orders will be printed and all other sales will be fully refunded, so no one will lose anything. You will be notified via email of which design was successful.

The aim of Innovate is to bring you designs limited to 50, so that not ever tom dick and harry are wearing it, due to the t-shirts being limited, to avoid disappointment it is best to order yours ASAP!!

Our t-shirts are Unisex, all printed on Gildan Softstyle Tees for maximum comfort. No girls fit are available, this is so you can do what ever you like to them, make them into dresses,vests or even tea towels.

Thanks for you help 
Scott x
